"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-sports-2024-8-6-frances-olympic-surfing-champ-vaast-says-life-force-helped-him-win-gold\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"France's Kauli Vaast, who rode his home wave in Polynesia to Olympic gold, says he got some extra spiritual help.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9942050428038595, \"rank\": 0.004209436534493391, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 20, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}, {\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 57, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9999999746153211, \"rank\": 2.5384730033814484e-08, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  Kauli Vaast says a supernatural force in Polynesian culture helped him win Olympic surfing gold in his native Tahiti.\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9992720534886992, \"rank\": 0.0007284768035449403, \"text\": \"Polynesian culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.5870916185981863, \"rank\": 0.703311660942827, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaast on Monday became the first Olympic champion from the French Pacific island.\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}, {\"begin\": 306, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9995410447422447, \"rank\": 0.0004425439259967163, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The mana was with me from the start, every day I felt it,\\\" the 22-year-old told AFP, referring to a supernatural force that, according to Polynesian beliefs, permeates the universe.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9996943216565263, \"rank\": 0.00028978676144623153, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9960861969130944, \"rank\": 0.001953993981987583, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not see it but I felt it, and 'voila', I did it - an Olympic champion,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaast beat Australia's Jack Robinson in the gold medal final, taking the two best waves of a high-level match.\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}, {\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.99758849473914, \"rank\": 0.0010913315102198122, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.8388520656682273, \"rank\": 0.18277340511020138, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}, {\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.8662285822138409, \"rank\": 0.1543236351999916, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The entire island rooted for him.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As soon as the first two waves were caught, we were all there blowing for there to be no more, and it worked,\\\" joked French Polynesia's President Moetai Brotherson.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moetai Brotherson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tahiti, with the majestic Teahupo'o waves that often reach 2-3 metres (6.5-10 feet) and sometimes a lot higher, hosted a spectacular surfing competition, which was extended until Monday due to unfavourable winds last week.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 919, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.5870916185981863, \"rank\": 0.703311660942827, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaast's mother, Natou Thupalua, opted for some garden therapy to calm her nerves.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When he competes in Tahiti, I garden,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.5870916185981863, \"rank\": 0.703311660942827, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I planted anthuriums.\\\"\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The newly crowned Olympic champion said he might need to do a bit of work in the garden now, too.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I get home, I am going to have to use the rake because she cut everything,\\\" he smiled.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thousands of Polynesians cheered their champion Johanne Defay from the French island of Reunion, who won bronze in the women's final.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9580229643298501, \"rank\": 0.025935520405423632, \"text\": \"Polynesians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johanne_Defay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Johanne Defay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johanne_Defay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johanne_Defay\"}, {\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Island_National_Park\", \"score\": 0.9975288938851635, \"rank\": 0.002178673114455573, \"text\": \"French island\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Island_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Island_National_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reunion_Records\", \"score\": 0.9999999999688498, \"rank\": 3.078927776292839e-11, \"text\": \"Reunion\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reunion_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reunion_Records\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three-time world champion Gabriel Medina of Brazil, who went into the Olympic Games as a widely tipped favourite, took the men's bronze.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Medina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surfing was introduced as an Olympic sport at the Tokyo 2020 Games and the success of the competition in Tahiti will help to further establish it on the programme.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.5870916185981863, \"rank\": 0.703311660942827, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tahiti, nearly 16,000 kilometres (9,940 miles) from Paris, was selected to host the second Olympic surfing competition in history with the aim of including France's overseas territories in the Games.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.5870916185981863, \"rank\": 0.703311660942827, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}, {\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 1989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999572642091, \"rank\": 4.273578157992173e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9942050428038595, \"rank\": 0.004209436534493391, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the surfing competition could prove a long-term bonus for Tahiti.\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.5870916185981863, \"rank\": 0.703311660942827, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic surfing event generated spectacular images and \\\"an extraordinary promotional operation\\\" for local tourism, said President Brotherson.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Winning on his home turf of Teahupo'o was \\\"the cherry on the cake\\\", Vaast said.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2419, \"end\": 2424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For all of France, for all of Polynesia, it's incredible.\\\"\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2443, \"end\": 2449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9942050428038595, \"rank\": 0.004209436534493391, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2462, \"end\": 2471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9999999746153211, \"rank\": 2.5384730033814484e-08, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": []}]}"